> ### * check_xpt_names
> 
> flush(stderr()); flush(stdout())
> 
> ### Name: check_xpt_names
> ### Title: Check column names for XPT compliance
> ### Aliases: check_xpt_names
> 
> ### ** Examples
> 
> df <- data.frame(`subject id` = 1, longcolumnname = 2, check.names = FALSE)
> check_xpt_names(df, version = 5)
        variable                                                         issue
1     subject id too long (10 > 8); not uppercase; contains invalid characters
2 longcolumnname                              too long (14 > 8); not uppercase
  suggested_name
1       SUBJECT_
2       LONGCOLU
> 
> 
> 
> 
