> ### Name: set_var_format
> ### Title: Set SAS format strings on a data frame
> ### Aliases: set_var_format
> 
> ### ** Examples
> 
> df <- data.frame(RFSTDTC = as.Date("2024-01-15"), AGE = 42L)
> df <- set_var_format(df, c(RFSTDTC = "DATE9.", AGE = "3."))
> get_var_format(df)
 RFSTDTC      AGE 
"DATE9."     "3." 
